6af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 942px) 100vw, 942px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-jpg.webp 942w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-276x300.webp 276w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.1ys7egh584l4-768x835.webp 768w" width="942" height="1024" /></a></p><p>招募时间：2024年6月21日（星期五）至2024年7月21日（星期日）</p><p>运营VTuber作品《.LIVE》的Upland将举办Upland虚拟人才选拔赛。通过试镜的人将获得30万日元作为活动经费。 Upland将承担创作原创角色的费用。除了借出配送所需的设备外，我们还计划为商业计划提供支持。欢迎条件包括格斗游戏、麻将、每周能够直播5次以上。</p><p> <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfL9Zp5ug21jXoZ12ahyz4ve4n8FV2GH0EGHM36IaUt-RHgXg/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://appland.co.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a></p><h2 id="link2">视频制作</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.c7g1cn9h5jcp-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>申请时间：～7月14日（周日）23:59（根据申请情况，申请可能会提前结束）</p><p> <a href="https://x.com/vdolproduction" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vdol Production</a>是一家专门针对西班牙语国家的 VTuber 机构，目前正在进行西班牙语 VTuber 活动的初始会员试镜。</p><p>申请人必须年满 18 岁、讲西班牙语、每周至少直播 5 次且活跃时间至少 1 年。通过试镜者将获得VTuber原创模特、发行设备租赁、营销支持等。</p><p>此外，以宇宙飞船船长为灵感的角色已作为招募角色发布。</p><p> <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfUOTwbiW9kUFOfgWmgODA-yEbFnVZ4RdmJVWRVm4vFpRkpmw/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000001.000145288.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vdol制作新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link3">MRT宫崎放送官方 宫崎本地VTuber</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.qsp2a2h3c138-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.qsp2a2h3c138-1024x538.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.qsp2a2h3c138-1024x538.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.qsp2a2h3c138-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.qsp2a2h3c138-768x403.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/9b66af5dc1645e86f038d79e8b2c95d1-kix.qsp2a2h3c138-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="538" /></a></p><p>招募时间：6月14日（周五）至7月15日（周一）</p><p> MRT宫崎放送授权的宫崎当地VTuber选拔正在进行中。</p><p>试镜结束后，活动预计于2024年11月左右开始。出道后，他们将参加捷运宫崎广播的节目、传播该地区魅力的直播活动以及宣传和营销支持活动等活动。</p><p><a href="https://unibirth.live/audition/mrt-202406/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000013.000115621.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Universe Production Co. 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link4">Activ8/Asobi System 联合项目“ANNIN”</h2><p> <a href="https://a